type":"entry","text":"angelfish [ˈeɪndʒlfɪʃ]","headword":"angelfish"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.神仙鱼（一种观赏用热带鱼）"},{"type":"text","text":"black tetra"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.黑裙鱼"},{"type":"text","text":"tiger barb"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.虎皮鱼"},{"type":"text","text":"zebra danio"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.斑马鱼"},{"type":"entry","text":"guppy [ˈɡʌpi]","headword":"guppy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.孔雀鱼"},{"type":"entry","text":"anemone [əˈneməni]","headword":"anemone"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.海葵"}]},{"number":1848,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"sea weed 海草","headword":"sea weed"},{"type":"entry","text":"fish food 鱼食","headword":"fish food"},{"type":"entry","text":"ectotherm [ˈektəʊθɜːm]","headword":"ectotherm"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.冷血动物"},{"type":"entry","text":"fishy [ˈfɪʃi]","headword":"fishy"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.鱼的，鱼味的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎fishy smell鱼腥味"},{"type":"entry","text":"scaled [skeɪld]","headword":"scaled"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.有鳞的；去鳞的"},{"type":"entry","text":"oviparous [əʊˈvɪpərəs]","headword":"oviparous"}]},{"number":1849,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"a.卵生的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎oviparous fish卵生鱼类"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词fish"},{"type":"text","text":"“鱼”在国内是一个受欢迎的字，餐桌上一条红烧鲤鱼，意味着“鲤"},{"type":"text","text":"鱼跳龙门”或者“年年有余（鱼）”。在美国也有不少习语跟fish有关，"},{"type":"text","text":"例如don't fish in the trouble water，就是“别浑水摸鱼”的意思。"},{"type":"text","text":"1. I'm fishing for an answer. 我正在摸索答案。"},{"type":"entry","text":"Fish for的意思是“设法用间接手段得到某物”，相当于try to gain","headword":"Fish for"},{"type":"text","text":"sth. by indirect methods。"},{"type":"text","text":"2. He's too much of a cold fish. 他实在是个很不友好的人。"},{"type":"entry","text":"A cold fish是指“对人很冷淡、很不友好的人”。","headword":"A cold fish"},{"type":"text","text":"3. I'm like a fish out of water here. 我在这儿感到很不适应。"},{"type":"text","text":"中国人常常用“如鱼得水”来形容一切都非常顺利的环境，而一旦"},{"type":"text","text":"鱼儿离了水（a fish out of water），当然就比较糟糕。这一习语常用来"},{"type":"text","text":"表示“不合时宜，格格不入，局促不安”。"}]}]}